  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>One day the sky came falling down, ripping the world apart. All creatures used to live together in harmony. But after the fall, many Creatures turned on the others. A Father who lost his family in this event by a powerful entity seeks revenge against the one behind it all. From then on, he sees all creatures as enemies. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Along his path he comes across many people that would help him on his revenge quest. Though not many fighters remain.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521650/extras/c2bfc93e6aae434567842c5cabf0c90a.webp?t=1774521074\" width=200 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Explore the different areas in the world of Trek.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521650/extras/1157c8428c4c5371597209c962f193f2.poster.avif?t=1774521074\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521650/extras/1157c8428c4c5371597209c962f193f2.webm?t=1774521074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521650/extras/1157c8428c4c5371597209c962f193f2.mp4?t=1774521074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521650/extras/67b03f66dd42caad40a157a95513330a.webp?t=1774521074\" width=200 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Invent countless creative combos.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521650/extras/4d28d6f708df6405f6cee0de106536d7.poster.avif?t=1774521074\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521650/extras/4d28d6f708df6405f6cee0de106536d7.webm?t=1774521074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521650/extras/4d28d6f708df6405f6cee0de106536d7.mp4?t=1774521074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521650/extras/c77f280dabd8984e15ec9be3257882c7.webp?t=1774521074\" width=200 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Huge and expanding pool of items.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521650/extras/5c0c8345b7aa94c51e867f0818013dc4.poster.avif?t=1774521074\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521650/extras/5c0c8345b7aa94c51e867f0818013dc4.webm?t=1774521074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521650/extras/5c0c8345b7aa94c51e867f0818013dc4.mp4?t=1774521074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.ste